    dc:description "FIGURES 44 − 49. Steleops mendivili n. sp. Male. 44. Fore wing and hind wing. 45. Side view of genitalia: Clunium, paraprocts-epiproct and hypandrium. 46. Front view of head. 47. Paraprocts and epiproct. 48. Phallosome. 49. Hypandrium. Scales in mm." ;
